<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main>
            <div class="container">
                <section class="about-section">
                    <h1>About Health & Fitness Tracker</h1>

                    <div class="about-content">
                        <h2>Your Personal Fitness Companion</h2>
                        <p>
                            Health & Fitness Tracker helps you log and monitor your fitness activities in one place. 
                            Whether you're going for a run, hitting the gym, or trying a new yoga class, we've got you covered. 
                            Track your progress, see your statistics, and stay motivated on your health journey.
                        </p>

                        <h2>What You Can Do</h2>
                        <ul class="features-list">
                            <li>Log various fitness activities with duration, distance, and calories burned</li>
                            <li>Keep your activities private or share them with others</li>
                            <li>Search and filter your activity history to find exactly what you're looking for</li>
                            <li>View detailed statistics about your fitness progress</li>
                            <li>Manage your account securely with email verification</li>
                        </ul>

                        <h2>Getting Started</h2>
                        <p>
                            It's simple: create an account, start logging your activities, and watch your fitness story unfold. 
                            You control what's private and what's public. All your data is secure and always under your control.
                        </p>

                        <div class="cta-section">
                            <h3>Ready to Start Your Fitness Journey?</h3>
                            <% if (!user) { %>
                                <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary">Register Now</a>
                                <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-secondary">Login</a>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <a href="/add-activity" class="btn btn-primary">Add Your First Activity</a>
                                    <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>